        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-02-19T13:25:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Add a reminder that matrix multiplication is associative, so the order of multiplication is arbitrary and does not matter:\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matrix_multiplication#Associativity",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 151,
        "startChar": 76,
        "endLine": 151,
        "endChar": 89
      },
      "revId": "3a9decc339c8b2039f074599bec62aedaf1141df",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "c9ecd2c0_6a3f2da3",
        "filename": "modules/canvaskit/interface.js",
        "patchSetId": 6
      },
      "lineNbr": 151,
      "author": {
        "id": 9065
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-02-19T20:43:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "But the order of the arguments does matter because it\u0027s not commutative.",
      "parentUuid": "d8b1f894_c25bdf47",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 151,
        "startChar": 76,
        "endLine": 151,
        "endChar": 89
      },
      "revId": "3a9decc339c8b2039f074599bec62aedaf1141df",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "d7e8ad48_503960bf",
        "filename": "modules/canvaskit/interface.js",
        "patchSetId": 6
      },
      "lineNbr": 151,
      "author": {
        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-02-19T21:11:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "order of arguments does matter. If we multiply them left to right or right to left, *that* does not matter",
      "parentUuid": "c9ecd2c0_6a3f2da3",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 151,
        "startChar": 76,
        "endLine": 151,
        "endChar": 89
